beer.beer_description: Unleash the darkness within… This dunkelweizen is chock-full of fresh, sweet cherries and ripe with banana esters. The finest German Munich, Crystal and wheat malts load this dark-hued beer up with biscuit and caramel notes. The addition of cherries late in the fermentation process brings a subtle sweetness and tang to this unique wheat beer.
